comments: Poeltl (SAS) reaches in and makes marginal contact to Embiid's (PHI) arm, the contact does not affect his ability to make the pass.
Murray (SAS) makes marginal contact with Korkmaz' (PHI) arm that does not affect his shot near the rim.
Korkmaz (PHI) legally contests White's (SAS) jump shot attempt.  Any "high-five" contact after the release is considered incidental.
Embiid (PHI) extends his leg and initiates marginal contact with Poeltl (SAS).
Korkmaz (PHI) moves laterally into Johnson (SAS) and initiates body contact that affects his driving shot attempt.
Embiid (PHI) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Murray (SAS), firms up and absorbs the contact.
White (SAS) makes contact to Maxey's (PHI) wrist and affects his control of the ball.
Walker IV (SAS) makes contact with Embiid's (PHI) arm that affects his driving shot attempt.
Poeltl (SAS) is not established in a screening position in Korkmaz's (PHI) path and delivers contact to his side that affects his ability to defend around the screen.
Poeltl (SAS) commits a take foul on Maxey (PHI).
